{"tid":148131,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"物理jj入（求指點）","createTime":"2017-03-08T11:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T13:27:40.000Z","uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cf76ee17381bcb0703f832dd5cd723f33eb58303","tid":148131,"uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:04:55.000Z","msg":"做一個柱體（比如圓柱體）,兩底面與帶電平板平行,通過這個柱體閉合曲面的電通量就等於通過兩底面的,等於 2 E*S<br />\n根據高斯定理,<span style=\"color: red;\">等於閉合曲面所包圍的電荷除以&epsilon;0,即 &sigma;S/&epsilon;0</span><br />\n2 E*S = &sigma;S/&epsilon;0<br />\n得 E = &sigma;/（2&epsilon;0）<br />\n<br />\n咁總共有圓柱有兩個面 &sigma;S=1個面<br />\n點解唔係&sigma;2S/&epsilon;0"},{"pid":"35c49bfca3e1bc4798ae9f0e2a1ee862139c6116","tid":148131,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3630116a45bc3611eed6eedb19dcd528821c8013","tid":148131,"uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:07:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做一個柱體（比如圓柱體）,兩底面與帶電平板平行,通過這個柱體閉合曲面的電通量就等於通過兩底面的,等於 2 E*S<br />\n根據高斯定理,<span style=\"color: red;\">等於閉合曲面所包圍的電荷除以&epsilon;0,即 &sigma;S/&epsilon;0</span><br />\n2 E*S = &sigma;S/&epsilon;0<br />\n得 E = &sigma;/（2&epsilon;0）<br />\n<br />\n咁總共有圓柱有兩個面 &sigma;S=1個面<br />\n點解唔係&sigma;2S/&epsilon;0</blockquote><br />\n講得唔清楚<br />\n<br />\n&sigma;=1個m有幾多q 咁&sigma;S=1個面既q數量 2個面=&sigma;2S/&epsilon;0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁諗有冇錯"},{"pid":"03cb30480a5994ddb44c89d8c88e2d93616ecff1","tid":148131,"uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:07:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小弟廢j 救下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be8c14af546daddd4edfb3370bab7b777489ae4","tid":148131,"uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0