sigma;會唔同</blockquote><br />\nSa 同Sb先岩"},{"pid":"f78056e1e003c232d7652807afafbde847c0e5e8","tid":148131,"uid":85839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:17:00.000Z","msg":"因為係個柱體入面<br />\n個Gaussian surface contain 既charges 係同個圓柱既半徑成正比"},{"pid":"9e5dfce1acd4ff345b454f79140c1bd393a710f5","tid":148131,"uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:20:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為係個柱體入面<br />\n個Gaussian surface contain 既charges 係同個圓柱既半徑成正比</blockquote><br />\n兩邊既r唔係相同咩 只係正負號唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77c3651f33fd900f11d2cf49ec5497b63dc3b89","tid":148131,"uid":85839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:27:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為係個柱體入面<br />\n個Gaussian surface contain 既charges 係同個圓柱既半徑成正比</blockquote><br />\n兩邊既r唔係相同咩 只係正負號唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔係好明你問咩<br />\n第一 個兩個帶電既面係帶咩電荷<br />\n第兩 其實Gaussian law講緊既係<br />\nIn(E) dot dA=charge enclosed / permittivity <br />\nE 同 dA都係一支vector 要考慮方向的<br />\n你show出黎個幅圖 講緊既野同你問個d野好似有出入"}]}